%% Requirement invariants (see docs/REQUIREMENTS.md)
mindmap
  root((STRATUM INV))
    INV-01 Coverage
      Senior intake blocked below floor
      Junior exit blocked if breaks floor
    INV-02 Senior protection
      Buffer pays IL first
      maxSeniorILExposureBps cap
    INV-03 Junior first loss
      IL reduces junior payout
      Reserve not double-debited
    INV-04 Waterfall
      Senior obligation before junior surplus
    INV-05 Buffer integrity
      Only epoch IL and shortfall draw reserve
    INV-06 Epoch monotonic
      currentEpoch only increases
      EpochNotElapsed on early close
